"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-showbiz-tom-cruise-paris-closing-ceremony-olympic-games-b1174356.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Showbiz  Sign up to our free weekly newsletter for exclusive competitions, offers and theatre ticket deals    I would like to be emailed about offers, event and updates from Evening Standard.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 420, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourprivacy notice.\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom Cruiseis set to add a dash ofHollywoodglamour to the Olympic Games closing ceremony, sources close to the event are said to have revealed.\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 588, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 62-year-old action star, famed for his death-defying stunts in the Mission: Impossible franchise, is reportedly filming a pre-recorded segment that will bridge the gap between Paris 2024 and the upcomingLos AngelesGames in 2028.\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 770, \"end\": 780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.981993027519947e-30, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to American entertainment websiteTMZ, Cruise's segment will see him rappelling down the Stade de France in Paris before jetting across the Atlantic to Los Angeles, where he will finish his journey at the iconic Hollywood sign.\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 837, \"end\": 845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9996593221893894, \"rank\": 0.0002506350285303928, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 941, \"end\": 946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.808671220286357e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 985, \"end\": 996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3292920976032755e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 1045, \"end\": 1059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The segment is expected to form part of the traditional Olympic flag handover, where Paris Mayor Anne Hidalgo will pass the Olympic flag to her Los Angeles counterpart, Karen Bass.\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1147, \"end\": 1158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Mayor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1159, \"end\": 1171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}, {\"begin\": 1206, \"end\": 1217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3292920976032755e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 1231, \"end\": 1241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Karen Bass\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While official details of the August 11 ceremony remain tightly under wraps, industry insiders have hinted at a spectacular show.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One source told Deadline, the respected Hollywood trade publication, to expect \\\"a major Hollywood production\\\".\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1414, \"end\": 1423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.8797504950863396e-12, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1462, \"end\": 1471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.