2, \"end\": 1895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.73215543202983e-28, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1946, \"end\": 1951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.808671220286357e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This would not be Cruise's first brush with Olympic glory.\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 2025, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2011, \"end\": 2024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Glory\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympic glory\", \"types\": [\"Q7377\", \"Q729\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Glory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Glory\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The actor helped carry the torch through Los Angeles for the 2004 Games, as part of the ceremonial relay across the globe before the Athens opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2067, \"end\": 2078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3292920976032755e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 2159, \"end\": 2165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"score\": 0.9626070865673129, \"rank\": 0.03884545828577318, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Los Angeles, set to host its third Summer Olympics from 14-30 July 2028, plans to utilise a mix of historic and modern venues.\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2311, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2185, \"end\": 2196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3292920976032755e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Emerald Fennell is an auteur of rage-bait - and we are all falling for it  Teyana Taylor not mystery person Leonardo DiCaprio was talking to in viral video  Kiefer Sutherland arrested on suspicion of assaulting LA ride-share driver  Incredible days out and trips for autumn and winter  Events will kick off at the Coliseum, built for the 1932 Games, and take place across the Downtown Sports Park, including the Crypto.com Arena and Microsoft Theater.\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2313, \"end\": 2328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emerald_Fennell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emerald Fennell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emerald_Fennell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emerald_Fennell\"}, {\"begin\": 2388, \"end\": 2401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teyana_Taylor\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Teyana Taylor\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teyana_Taylor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teyana_Taylor\"}, {\"begin\": 2421, \"end\": 2438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_DiCaprio\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Leonardo DiCaprio\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_DiCaprio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_DiCaprio\"}, {\"begin\": 2470, \"end\": 2487, \"ti